1. Postgres resouce manager (on linux we can use cgroup) like oracle resouce manager
2. Postgres AWR package (ASH , V$SQL_MONIOR , SQL_ID , AWR Report , ...)
3. Use OCI (Oracle Call Interface) to build a high performance Oracle to REST like (ORDS)
4. Call C program from Oracle with procedure
5. Oracle Goldengate USEREXIT high performace notifier for transaction

